{"TopicId":204423,"ForumId":44,"TopicTitle":"What do you think about Jeff Bezos suing NASA?","CreatedByName":"Pawelk198604","CreatedById":35539,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-20T02:11:03Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Pawelk198604","CreatedById":35539,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-20T02:11:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCould the fact that Jeff Bezos just sued NASA over the exclusion of Blue Origin from the contract to build the lunar lander delay the implementation of the entire lunar program?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JoeSchmuckatelli","CreatedById":154477,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-20T02:19:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are quite a few discussions about this in both the BO and SX threads.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEnjoy!\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Beccab","CreatedById":208000,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-20T04:11:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224022078\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204423\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221629425463\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002235539\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Pawelk198604\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Pawelk198604 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCould the fact that Jeff Bezos just sued NASA over the exclusion of Blue Origin from the contract to build the lunar lander delay the implementation of the entire lunar program?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s the intention\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-20T13:02:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224022104\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204423\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221629432711\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022208000\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Beccab\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, Beccab said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s the intention\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think the intention is to jam their foot in the door before Starship functions at any level. Once SS is a thing, their own lander is an overpriced toy, and it clearly makes no sense to use it. If they have a contract in place, it gets to be built even though it will be silly. Imagine the astronauts given a choice, do you want to spend a week\u002B on the Moon living/eating/eliminating with 3 other people inside something the size of an SUV, or would you prefer to go and bring a 4 bedroom house with you?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr think about trying to sell that to NASA. \u0022Yeah, we\u0027re offering a tiny faction of the capability, but it\u0027s only 3X the price!\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbart","CreatedById":78303,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-20T13:15:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224022226\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204423\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221629464529\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022119411\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022tater\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 minutes ago, tater said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think the intention is to jam their foot in the door before Starship functions at any level. Once SS is a thing, their own lander is an overpriced toy, and it clearly makes no sense to use it. If they have a contract in place, it gets to be built even though it will be silly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe speed at which SpaceX develops things is incredible. Bezos is right with wanting to get in \u003Cem\u003Enow\u003C/em\u003E. A year from now SpaceX is probably already landing on the moon. ULA has a \u0022proven track record\u0022 argument to justify higher costs. BO has pretty much nothing. If you can\u0027t compete on price, or merit, go to court!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Silavite","CreatedById":156204,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-20T14:15:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224022229\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204423\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221629465331\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278303\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerbart\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n56 minutes ago, Kerbart said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe speed at which SpaceX develops things is incredible. Bezos is right with wanting to get in \u003Cem\u003Enow\u003C/em\u003E. A year from now SpaceX is probably already landing on the moon. ULA has a \u0022proven track record\u0022 argument to justify higher costs. BO has pretty much nothing. If you can\u0027t compete on price, or merit, go to court!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is an old legal adage\u00A0that says,\u00A0\u0022If you have the facts on your side, pound the facts; if you have the law on your side, pound the law; if you have neither the facts nor the law, pound the table.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUnfortunately, I think that BO is pounding the table at this point.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-20T14:24:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are always lawsuits, this is \u0027Murica, after all.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DDE","CreatedById":146349,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-20T14:25:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224022229\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204423\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221629465331\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278303\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerbart\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Kerbart said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBO has pretty much nothing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBO is ULA in a New Space get-up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022E2qYoIDWUAgeV5X.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022800\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://pbs.twimg.com/media/E2qYoIDWUAgeV5X.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbart","CreatedById":78303,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-20T15:11:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224022226\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204423\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221629464529\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022119411\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022tater\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, tater said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf they have a contract in place, it gets to be built even though it will be silly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSurely congress would put an end to such waste of money if it\u2019s pointless.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRight? Right?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n[sound of crickets]\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JoeSchmuckatelli","CreatedById":154477,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-20T15:38:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224022280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204423\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221629472273\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278303\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerbart\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n26 minutes ago, Kerbart said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSurely congress would put an end to such waste of money if it\u2019s pointless.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRight? Right?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n[sound of crickets]\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSnark.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCongress does have to abide by the contract terms... but usually there are exit clauses.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-20T15:39:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224022255\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204423\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221629469528\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022146349\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DDE\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, DDE said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBO is ULA in a New Space get-up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003EReally\u003C/em\u003E unfair to ULA. ULA builds and flies highly capable vehicles with high reliability. BO flies nothing substantial at all, and is not on track to demonstrate they are even capable of it for a few years.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224022280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204423\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221629472273\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278303\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerbart\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n28 minutes ago, Kerbart said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSurely congress would put an end to such waste of money if it\u2019s pointless.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRight? Right?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n[sound of crickets]\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLOL\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MKI","CreatedById":77241,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-20T18:26:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224022249\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204423\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221629468925\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022156204\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Silavite\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, Silavite said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is an old legal adage\u00A0that says,\u00A0\u0022If you have the facts on your side, pound the facts; if you have the law on your side, pound the law; if you have neither the facts nor the law, pound the table.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is great, writing this one down.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mr.dobsonian","CreatedById":213739,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-31T22:43:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe reason the ocean is salty is because Jeff went for a swim one time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-08-31T22:44:08Z\u0022 title=\u002208/31/2021 10:44  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 31, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Mr.dobsonian\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"wumpus","CreatedById":133850,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-01T14:43:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224022249\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204423\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221629468925\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022156204\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Silavite\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 8/20/2021 at 10:15 AM, Silavite said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is an old legal adage\u00A0that says,\u00A0\u0022If you have the facts on your side, pound the facts; if you have the law on your side, pound the law; if you have neither the facts nor the law, pound the table.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUnfortunately, I think that BO is pounding the table at this point.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey are going beyond that, and bringing in their best lobbyists.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://arstechnica.com/science/2021/09/blue-origin-hires-advisory-firm-linked-to-messy-jedi-contract-process/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://arstechnica.com/science/2021/09/blue-origin-hires-advisory-firm-linked-to-messy-jedi-contract-process/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DDE","CreatedById":146349,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-01T19:51:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224026828\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204423\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221630507407\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022133850\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022wumpus\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, wumpus said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://arstechnica.com/science/2021/09/blue-origin-hires-advisory-firm-linked-to-messy-\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://arstechnica.com/science/2021/09/blue-origin-hires-advisory-firm-linked-to-messy-\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Ejedi\u003C/strong\u003E-contract-process/\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSomething something Order 66 meme\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StrandedonEarth","CreatedById":89439,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-02T00:32:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedOther\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed6906446677\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?app=core\u0026amp;module=system\u0026amp;controller=embed\u0026amp;url=https://twitter.com/spacexmr/status/1433144821703757827?s=21\u0022 style=\u0022height:591px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"lajoswinkler","CreatedById":79159,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-02T14:45:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat do I think? I think it\u0027s both pathetic and hilarious and should be dismissed as frivolous lawsuit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-02T15:00:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs Bezos\u0027s launch site situated in a place full of crocosaurs, too?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf no, they should also set zoo defenders on BocaChica, for frying the helpless crocos alive.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-09-02T15:00:35Z\u0022 title=\u002209/02/2021 03:00  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 2, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Maria Sirona","CreatedById":210882,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-06T14:28:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLet\u0027s be honest, Who is a sore loser\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}